{{- /* 
============================================================================
JSON Configuration Template
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
This template generates a JSON configuration file with secrets organized
under a section. It creates a structured JSON object that can be used by
applications that read JSON configuration files.

Usage:
  - Include this file in your application configuration
  - Access values using JSON parsing libraries
  - The template expects data with: { Section: string, Items: map[string]string }
  - Example output creates JSON config with sectioned secrets

Security:
  - JSON files may contain sensitive configuration data
  - Use appropriate access controls for configuration files
  - Do NOT commit generated files with real secrets to version control

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Template logic:
  - Creates a JSON object with a section key
  - Places all secrets under the section as key-value pairs
============================================================================
*/ -}}
{
  "{{.Section}}": {{.Items | toJSON}}
}
